OL,4,CBrazil's Amazon: Deforestation rises
OL,5,Cahead of dry season
OL,6, Deforestation of the Amazon rainforest
OL,7, in Brazil rose by 43% in April compared
OL,8, to the same month last year, government
OL,9, data has shown.
OL,11,FA total of 1,157 sq km (446 sq miles)
OL,12,Fof rainforest were destroyed in the
OL,13,Ffirst four months of 2021. This was
OL,14,Fdown 4% from a year earlier.
OL,16,FThe Amazon is a vital carbon store that
OL,17,Fslows down the pace of global warming.
OL,19,FScientists say the loss of forest has
OL,20,Faccelerated since Brazilian President
OL,21,FJair Bolsonaro took office in 2019.
